textAfterTable: m = morning e = evening - Room reservations are out for these 7 rooms ( 4 single and 3 shared). - This reservation is confirmed by LinuxHotel. [edit] Costs Per person for the location: 5 euro per person per day for the conference room -> 3 days * 5 euro = 15 euro 15 euro per person per night for a double room -> 2 nights * 15 euro = 30 euro or 30 euro per person per night for a single room -> 2 nights * 30 euro = 60 euro 5 euro per person per day for the breakfast -> 2 (sat, sun) * 5 = 10 euro 5 euro per person for the cleaning -> 5 euro These costs are payed by the eV directly. You need to pay for all the food and drinks not included in the price above. Rumors say beer is included ;-) All those payments are not refundable. Travel costs are refundable, by filling out the form from: http://ev.kde.org/resources/expense_report.pdf For Igor there has been made a special arrangement.
